{"tid":1864477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞] 廁所無廁紙 新屋唔住得？ 東姑：屙完就應洗屎忽","createTime":"2020-02-05T15:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T15:55:16.000Z","uid":35070,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"56fca0d4c1b407d6b5e07476179425e93e1de991","tid":1864477,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:27:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cemeterynews.org/2017/01/22/tunku/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcemeterynews.org%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2Ftunku%2F&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iStw7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=0485cdc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://cemeterynews.org/2017/01/22/tunku/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5a/Tunku_abd_rahman.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F5%2F5a%2FTunku_abd_rahman.jpg&h=a39e7ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有指香港前政務司司長驚覺便利店並無廁紙發售，馬來西亞國父，首相東姑鴨都拉曼（Tunku Abdul Rahman Putra Al-Haj ibni Almarhum Sultan Abdul Hamid Shah，1903-1990）特意聯絡本報，希望向香港人介紹馬來西亞的廁所佈局。<br />\n<br />\n他指，在馬來西亞的廁所，是設有一條水喉，方便在如廁後直接清洗屁股，東姑稱：「這不單方便，而且令痔瘡發病率減少，林太這麼大年紀，沒見過這些東西嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東姑鴨都拉曼補充：「在水資源豐富的國度，用水洗屁股不過份呀。你們香港貴價買入、年年傾倒的東江水這麼多，不試試用來洗直腸、洗屁股？」他臉上掛著一副不解的神情，並指：「夜裏喚車不是更加浪費嗎？這樣的官真好當，你之前支的薪水不是百姓的血汗嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n記者問東姑國父有沒有補充，他指有：「在日本老早就懂得在廁所板上加設便後清洗風乾器，你們的城市不是很先進的嗎？怎麼還為一圈小小的廁紙苦惱呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/06.imgmini.eastday.com/mobile/20180604/20180604165331_4fdb1b869a3384db5b64ec3afe74339b_2.jpeg?w&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2F06.imgmini.eastday.com%2Fmobile%2F20180604%2F20180604165331_4fdb1b869a3384db5b64ec3afe74339b_2.jpeg%3Fw%26ssl%3D1&h=f143fc0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5d0ee90a37b8425a40d3729a0a086c35162d3fa","tid":1864477,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1416e2e7bb13fe6a6562e4017aaea658be1bef","tid":1864477,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />裝咗好耐，紙巾都冇乜點用"},{"pid":"208e12f9658d5a188bebe5afc2435f759a2ecbb2","tid":1864477,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735bf9317ae146c38c48ffbb449db190c85b4bdc","tid":1864477,"uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:40:30.000Z","msg":"其實咪成地屎水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6a7192d5dce7d303de0ef6e2e75421ca205668","tid":1864477,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:42:21.000Z","msg":"想試好耐，但無勇氣試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幻想一下，你點刻意去避啲水免整濕條底褲或褲？<br />\n除咗呢點，會唔會噴撚到成個下身都係屎水？<br />\n除非成條底褲或褲除晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5689572e616feddff2ccbceee3fd24857443d5","tid":1864477,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"735bf9317ae146c38c48ffbb449db190c85b4bdc","tid":1864477,"uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:40: